race.comment: Tough. AUCKLAND (3) came back to the turf and turned the form around winning at Echuca this grade and a short price favourite. That stacks up for this, and he will push forward and take beating again. SHE IS ALL MAGIC (10) disappointed on the same day over 1200m but missed a nose here prior over this distance. She deserves another chance. NIETZSCHE (8) resumes and is best on the fresh side. Draws the inside barrier and has a handy 2kg claim. He's in the mix. DERELICT (1) didn't feature in stronger at Mornington but missed a nose from the pace at Casterton prior. Uses an inside gate and has claims in a more suitable assignment. MAGIC DRUM (2) resumes and is proven fresh. Placed in a recent jumpout and monitor the betting with him.
